Apun his scouting in beast mode waspinator spotted the McGowan group 
and the Insecticons both heading towards the predacon base, the bug 
then flew back to the base and into the bridge "Megatron, two strage 
looking armies come, Waspinator think they heading towards base but 
not know how they know where base is" Waspinator said to Megatron

Inferno dragged the broken off thruster as well as some computer 
parts back to the base "Royalty I have retriaved all of the still 
functional parts of the colony back"

"So where do ya find energon anyway?" Quickstrike asked.
